Anna Q. Nilsson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anna_Q._Nilsson 0 Anna Quirentia Nilsson (March 30, 1888 – February 11, 1974) was a Swedish-born American actress who achieved success in American silent movies. She predates fellow Swedish born Astars Greta Garbo and Ingrid Bergman.
